des: Marilyn Horton has an enthusiasm for seeing people achieve great things through her winning attitude and optimism. Every day, Alexa users will enjoy hearing Marilyn's energy come through as she inspires, educates, and leads listeners to a greater sense of self-worth, encouraging classic styling and social courtesies, as well as sharing organizational and business tips for a beautifully balanced best life!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
